<h1>DC UNIVERSE</H1>
<p>The DC Universe (DCU) is the fictional shared universe where the stories in most American comic book titles published by DC Comics take place. DC superheroes such as Superman, Batman, and The Flash and etc, are from this universe, and it also contains well known supervillains such as Lex Luthor, the Joker, Harley Quinn, and Gorrila Grodd. Note that in context, "DC Universe" is usually used to refer to the main DC continuity. Occasionally, "DC Universe" will be used to indicate the "DC Multiverse", the collection of all continuities within DC Comics publications.</p><br>
<center><img src="http://www.fanboy.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/dc_heroes_big.gif" width="50%"></center>
